description.narrative: UNICEF reached 434,844 mothers, fathers and caretakers of children with at least one session of IYCF counseling, 139,673 children 6-59 months received VAS; 140,330 children 6-24 months received multiple micronutrient powders; 286,646 PLWs received multiple micronutrient tablets; 8026 Community Workers have reached households with key interventions of health WASH and nutrition. As well, 50 mother to mother support groups has been trained in Puntland while seven father to father support groups were established among IDP communities. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
